lead_paragraph: McLaren boss Ron Dennis was at pains to point out on Saturday that Jenson Button was not retiring from Formula One at the end of the season but there are no guarantees the 2009 champion will race again either.

headline.print_headline: Button Not Retiring but May Not Race on Either
headline.main: Button Not Retiring but May Not Race on Either
